1.title: Music Video Showcase
1.plot: Hosted by Andrew Caravella, RetroRock-iT puts the spotlight on minor-stream musical artists, groups and actors. We consider the sometimes struggling minor-stream artist our hero(s) and strive to give them the credit they deserve. As it says on the opening credits, "We Play Everything". RetroRock-iT does not discriminate, meaning you can find just about every variety of music, show and entertainment here! imdb.plot outline: Retro Rock-It showcases underdog talents that perform cover and original songs that have had their works produced in a music video. The show appears as a contemporary version of the early day version or MTV's Total Request Live. Andrew plays the Carson Daly type host, getting intimate and personal with musicians from around the country.
